Texto: Hey there :) I don’t usually message first, but you looked kind.
Respuesta1: That’s sweet of you to say

Texto: Maybe a little ;) So… what brings you to this app?
Respuesta1: Just looking to meet new people

Texto: Haha, don’t push your luck. I’m just being nice.
Respuesta1: Guess I’ll have to earn that next message
Respuesta2: Then I’ll take the win and vanish ;)

Texto: Fair enough. I’m a single mom, so my time is... limited.
Respuesta2: Oh, so no wild nights out then?

Texto: I appreciate honesty, even if it’s not romantic haha.
Respuesta1: That’s me — honest to a fault

Texto: Yeah, it’s a lot, but my son keeps me grounded.
Respuesta1: You sound like a great mom
Respuesta2: Kids, huh? That’s... a lot of work.

Texto: It is work, but he’s worth every second.
Respuesta2: I guess I’m not ready for that kind of life.

Texto: I don’t get much adult conversation, so this is kinda nice.
Respuesta1: I’m glad I can give you that break

Texto: Haha maybe! It’s rare I get to just chat.
Respuesta1: Then let’s make it a good one
Respuesta2: Don’t let me keep you if you’re busy.

Texto: You’re actually easy to talk to. That’s rare on here.
It’s nice. I almost forgot what it felt like to talk without pressure.
Respuesta1: You deserve that kind of peace
Respuesta2: That’s the app magic before the awkward phase ;)

Texto: Haha, maybe! Still, you seem genuine.
Respuesta1: I try to be, especially with someone like you

Respuesta2: It’s not flattery if it’s true.

Texto: Careful, I might start believing you.
Respuesta1: Then let me prove I mean it

Texto: You’re funny… and actually kind of refreshing.

Texto: Haha, you did. Maybe we could grab coffee sometime?
